data.description: This 2 BD, 1 BA Old Fourth Ward Condo offers an array of amenities through its HOA, making it an attractive living space. Situated in the vibrant Old Fourth Ward neighborhood, known for its historical significance and modern urban lifestyle. The condo boasts high ceilings and hardwood flooring throughout, adding a touch of elegance and spaciousness to the living space. The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops, providing both functionality and style. Its layout allows for easy interaction with the family room. The family room features a wall of floor-to-ceiling windows, allowing ample natural light to flood the space and offering panoramic views of the surroundings. The bathroom is adorned with marble tile and features a tub inside the shower, combining luxury and convenience in one space. A separate laundry room adds practicality to the living space, providing a dedicated area for laundry chores. The primary bedroom offers ample space, featuring hardwood flooring, a walk-in closet, and access to a double glass door deck. A ceiling fan ensures comfort during warmer months. Residents have access to a variety of amenities, including a workout room, greenspace, and a swimming pool. These facilities provide opportunities for recreation, fitness, and relaxation without leaving the premises. The HOA dues include cable, high speed internet, concierge, sewer, water, gym, swimming, landscaping, reserve fund, pest control, reserve, gas. Overall, this condo combines modern comforts with convenient amenities, making it an ideal choice for those seeking a comfortable and enjoyable living space in the heart of Old Fourth Ward. Please inquire about the FHA assumable loan through PennyMAC.
